comp.sql:
SELECT
`satisfaction_level`,
 `quality_rating`,
 `category`,
 `gender`,
 `priority_group`,
 `feature_enabled`,
 `purchase_date`,
 `additional_notes`,
 `confirm_password`,
 `description`,
 `agree_terms`,
 `invoice_file_path`,
 `order_time`,
 `customerID`
FROM feedback_form
WHERE ({{input_search.value?.trim()}} = '' OR (`category` LIKE '%{{input_search.value?.trim()}}%'))
LIMIT {{table_data.pageSize}} OFFSET {{table_data.pageOffset}}

SELECT count(`customerID`) AS total_record
FROM feedback_form
WHERE ({{input_search.value?.trim()}} = '' OR (`category` LIKE '%{{input_search.value?.trim()}}%'))
